 {"id":"asupersync-1qfd0.146","title":"[audit][sync] Enforce Pool warmup_timeout across the warmup phase","description":"src/sync/pool.rs exposes PoolConfig::warmup_timeout as a phase-level timeout for GenericPool::warmup(), but the current implementation never enforces it and can wait forever on a stalled factory. Apply the timeout across the full warmup phase, preserve existing WarmupStrategy semantics (FailFast errors immediately, BestEffort returns partial progress, RequireMinimum errors only when the minimum was not reached), add focused regressions for timeout behavior, and validate with rch-backed cargo commands.","status":"in_progress","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","assignee":"DarkHawk","created_at":"2026-03-11T09:49:48.101659550Z","created_by":"DarkHawk","updated_at":"2026-03-11T09:56:14.021149334Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-1qfd0.146","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1qfd0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-11T09:49:48.101659550Z","created_by":"DarkHawk"}]}
